title: Jaishankar heads to France, aircraft engines, subs and Indo-Pacific on cards - Hindustan Times
content:
1. Jaishankar heads to France, aircraft engines, subs and Indo-Pacific on cards  Hindustan Times
  2. Jaishankar holds wide-ranging and productive talks with French counterpart in Paris  Moneycontrol
  3. Jaishankar on a 3-day visit to France; to attend EU Ministerial Forum for Cooperation in Indo-Pacific  Zee News
  4. EAM begins France visit; Talks to be held on Chinese aggression in Indo-Pacific, aircraft engines  Hindustan Times

description: Jaishankar will meet his French counterpart Jean Yves Le Drian, Minister for French Armed Forces Florence Parly and is expected to call on French President Emmanuel Macron. He will address a conference of EU Foreign Ministers on Indo-Pacific and hold a Head of Mission conference for Indian envoys in Europe
